sentences: Scott Hansen (born February 7, 1977), known professionally as Tycho ( TY-koh), is an American musician, record producer, composer, and songwriter based in San Francisco.
Tycho's first EP, titled The Science of Patterns, was released in 2002.
The first Tycho album, Past Is Prologue, was released in 2006.

Tycho signed to Mom+Pop and Ninja Tune in 2019 but has also released music on Ghostly International, Merck Records and Gammaphone Records.
The fourth studio album, Epoch, received a nomination for Best Dance/Electronic Album in the 2017 Grammy Awards.
Tycho received a second Grammy nomination for Best Dance/Electronic Album for his fifth studio album, Weather, in the 2020 Grammy Awards.
In February 2020, Tycho released Simulcast, an instrumental version of Weather he previously promised fans.
